656
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:53,480
I get it.

657
00:31:54,640 --> 00:31:55,559
I totally get it.

658
00:31:57,480 --> 00:32:00,519
A high wall separates lovers.

659
00:32:03,559 --> 00:32:04,799
You met someone?

660
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:08,200
From the women's prison next door.

661
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:10,319
The cutest one there.

662
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:12,279
The cutest one?

663
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,759
Good for you.

664
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:17,400
