692
00:33:25,408 --> 00:33:26,160
Fine, I won't eat.

693
00:33:26,519 --> 00:33:27,880
Then don't eat.

694
00:33:37,359 --> 00:33:38,039
Keep eating.

695
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:46,179
Sit down and eat.

696
00:33:57,920 --> 00:33:58,759
You can make a living

697
00:33:59,319 --> 00:34:01,039
out there if you master a skill.

698
00:34:03,279 --> 00:34:05,240
Muster the courage to start over.

699
00:34:06,119 --> 00:34:07,720
Lift your head like a lion.

700
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:10,039
Keep your heroic spirit.

701
00:34:10,760 --> 00:34:12,360
Grasp the essence and spirit.

702
00:34:12,599 --> 00:34:14,199
Keep these words in your heart.

703
00:34:14,199 --> 00:34:15,079
Go away.

704
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:16,599
What's wrong?

705
00:34:16,599 --> 00:34:17,519
