with the essay reader.

714
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:34,159
That guy is looking out for him.

715
00:34:34,599 --> 00:34:35,480
Keep up, will you?

716
00:34:35,760 --> 00:34:37,320
They're both pissing me off.

717
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:39,000
Keep up with the pace.

718
00:34:39,119 --> 00:34:39,639
Bro.

719
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:42,159
D-Didn't we just get in here?

720
00:34:43,079 --> 00:34:44,079
Don't cause trouble.

721
00:34:44,280 --> 00:34:45,199
Yeah, very good.

722
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:46,159
And also...

723
00:34:46,159 --> 00:34:47,199
