729
00:34:56,679 --> 00:34:57,519
You know?

730
00:34:58,039 --> 00:34:59,440
Let's not mess with him.

731
00:34:59,639 --> 00:35:00,559
You think I'm scared?

732
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,719
I'm a killer.
You think I'm scared of him?

733
00:35:02,719 --> 00:35:03,880
That's not what I meant.

734
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:04,800
Lu Sheng.

735
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:08,400
Help Chen Xiaobin.

736
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:09,840
Their lion looks awful.

737
00:35:10,639 --> 00:35:11,119
Okay.

738
00:35:12,760 --> 00:35:13,280
He Chuang.

739
00:35:13,639 --> 00:35:14,920
What are you doing?

740
00:35:15,079 --> 00:35:16,639
Don't you know your tail is missing?

741
00:35:16,639 --> 00:35:17,280
Chen Xiaobin.

742
00:35:18,559 --> 00:35:19,519
Come with us.

743
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:20,639
Alright.

744
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:22,679
Watch your step.

745
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:23,880
Stay steady.

746
00:35:24,519 --> 00:35:25,079
Left.

747
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:25,840
Right.

748
00:35:26,239 --> 00:35:27,519
Left, right,

749
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:28,280
left.

750
00:35:29,480 --> 00:35:30,760
- What are you doing?
- Stop it!

751
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:33,159
- Let him go.
- Stop fighting.

752
00:35:33,159 --> 00:35:34,400
- Hands on your head.
- Let go.

753
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:35,400
Squat down.

754
00:35:35,639 --> 00:35:36,519
Stop it. Squat down.

755
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:38,400
Go away.

756
00:35:39,159 --> 00:35:40,480
Huang Jiawang, I'll kill you.

757
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:40,960
Squat down.

758
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,199
Lu Sheng, what are you doing?

759
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:45,719
Squat down.

760
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,159
