761
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:58,079
Who hit you?

762
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:02,519
Report.

763
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:03,840
Speak.

764
00:36:04,360 --> 00:36:05,400
Huang Jiawang started it.

765
00:36:05,679 --> 00:36:06,760
Say it again.

766
00:36:08,039 --> 00:36:08,760
Behave.

767
00:36:09,056 --> 00:36:10,752
- Squat down.
- Confinement for three days.

768
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:12,480
Three days?

769
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:14,840
So what? Three days it is.

770
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,512
One more word,
