771
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:19,280
Don't move.

772
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:22,960
Wang, take Li Hui to the infirmary.

773
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:23,280
Okay.

774
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:23,960
Lu Sheng.

775
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:25,519
Come with me.

776
00:36:26,679 --> 00:36:27,159
Yes, sir.

777
00:36:30,079 --> 00:36:31,320
Don't you want to be released?

778
00:36:32,908 --> 00:36:33,840
