815
00:37:54,719 --> 00:37:55,800
Memorize mine first.

816
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:56,800
Go on.

817
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:57,519
Try again.

818
00:37:57,519 --> 00:37:58,000
1...

819
00:37:58,760 --> 00:37:59,480
That's about it.

820
00:38:00,639 --> 00:38:02,440
Wash up and get ready to rest.

821
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:03,599
Sir.

822
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:05,159
Sir.

823
00:38:05,159 --> 00:38:05,639
What?

824
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:08,000
Lend me a pen.

825
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:09,440
