876
00:40:57,639 --> 00:40:59,400
Otherwise, stay hungry.

877
00:41:04,719 --> 00:41:05,440
I'm not hungry.

878
00:41:08,119 --> 00:41:08,599
But

879
00:41:08,599 --> 00:41:09,920
I don't mind having some.

880
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:24,239
From now on,

881
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,760
