883
00:41:30,079 --> 00:41:31,960
If I see you starting a fight...

884
00:41:35,159 --> 00:41:36,960
You want to win me over just like that?

885
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:38,360
Are you serious?

886
00:41:41,320 --> 00:41:42,000
