893
00:42:10,639 --> 00:42:12,679
This is the last thing I'll say to you.

894
00:42:13,119 --> 00:42:14,239
From now on,

895
00:42:14,599 --> 00:42:15,960
during your seven days here,

896
00:42:17,239 --> 00:42:18,360
even if you want to talk,

897
00:42:18,599 --> 00:42:19,559
heed any advice,

898
00:42:20,079 --> 00:42:21,039
and reflect,

899
