We can't hear a bit of your roar.

903
00:42:29,599 --> 00:42:31,679
You can't hear any sound, either.

904
00:42:33,039 --> 00:42:34,159
Stay for seven days.

905
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:35,880
Enjoy it.

906
